	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihil plane opus fuerat tanta praefatione; nam ex animo tibi, mi domine et frater, inservio ideoque Defectum literis inclusum ad te mitto et iubeo te libere et sequre a me petere, quae a me tibi confecta petis; tibi et filio tuo d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p5454" cert="high">Iosueo</persName> libentissime, in quacunque re possum, inservio.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miror, an ultimas meas ad te literas acceperis; tradideram eas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2451" cert="high">Aptcellensi</placeName> cuidam, procero et cano viro, qui obambulans literas ferre et nuncia expedire solet; nam omnino puto illi me tradidisse literas ante 2 menses aut circiter, ni fallor.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Migravit sane ad dominum 14. huius mensis honestissima matrona <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4091" cert="high">Zvinglia</persName>, d. <persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltheri</persName> nostri uxor, magno omnium nostrum cum dolore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed audi, mi frater, quid praeterea evenerit.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mox sequuntur illam, quam impensissime dilexerunt, charissimae meae filiae duae, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6609" cert="high">Elisabetha</persName>, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8442" cert="high">Simleri</persName> mei uxor, et <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p7227" cert="high">Anna</persName>, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4091" cert="high">Zvinglii</persName> mei uxor.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Excessere intra dies 6, Elisabetha 20. novembris, cum decubuisset a 18., Anna vero 23., cum decubuisset sub vesperam 18. Mors harum maximum mihi conscivit moerorem; rursus tamen illud me consolatur egregie, quod syncera firmaque fide praeditae et in invocatione nominis Christi perseverarunt in extremum usque spiritum migrantes ex hoc saeculo vultu placido et hilari, nuspiam dimoventes oculos a me, qui precando et confirmando verbis Christi praeibam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alioqui valemus sic satis recte adhuc omnes, stamus tamen in procinctu et expectamus mente laeta vocationem domini cum gratia eius per omnia nos subiicientes divinae voluntati.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu ora pro nobis dominum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta diligentissime piissimos et doctissimos symmystas, fratres nostros.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Saluta filium tuum d. <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p5454">Iosueum</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1918" cert="high">Linerum</persName> et alios nostros amicos, imprimis senem <persName type="auto_name">Rüttlingerum</persName>, cui ex animo omnia felicia precor.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale aeternum, mi colendissime domine et frater charissime.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri ultima novembris 1565.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1789" cert="high">Ioanni Kesslero</persName>, ludi literarii <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l474" cert="high">Sangallensis</placeName> moderatori fidelissimo, domino meo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l474" cert="high">Sangallen</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
